  $( Pascal's rule for the binomial coefficient, generalized to all integers
     ` K ` .  Equation 2 of [Gleason] p. 295.  (Revised by Mario Carneiro,
     10-Mar-2014.) $)
  bcpasc $p |- ( ( N e. NN0 /\ K e. ZZ ) ->
                ( ( N _C K ) + ( N _C ( K - 1 ) ) ) = ( ( N + 1 ) _C K ) ) $=
