    opreq12d opreq2 opreq1 eqeq12d syl5ibrcom simpr opreq1i syl6eleq cn nn0p1nn
    addid2 nnuz fzm1 biimpa sylan nn0cn pncan sylancl eleq2d 1nn0 eleqtri fzss1
    wss mpan ssel2 bcp1n syldan wne crp bcrpcl rpcn nncn a1i elfzelz adantl zcn
    addsub cle elfzle2 nn0z znn0sub syl2anc mpbid eqeltrd nnne0 div12 syl112anc
    nnrp rpdivcl mulcom eqtrd npcan adddi 3eqtr2d divcan1 elfznn divdiv2 subsub
    syl122anc bcm1k eqtr4d opreq1d fzelp1 nnz elfzm1b syl2anr eleqtrd sylan9eqr
    bcnn imp wn con3d bcval3 cvv rpne0 divmul3 mpbird div23 3eqtr3rd nn0re ltp1
    3eqtrrd olcd mpd3an23 jaodan jaod sylbid adantlr simpll simplr fzssp1 sseld
    ex 00id peano2zm id oprex fzp1ss eqsstr3i sseli syl6bir sylbird pm2.61dan )
